ealth may affect long-term).\n\nOverall, which candidate best balances? B seems strong on reliability (conscientious), stress handling, weather assessment (critical for long flights), computer skills (modern avionics). Weaknesses: pretentious, tone issues - could affect crew communication but maybe manageable. Others have more severe communication issues (A unfriendly, C difficulty communicating, D loner). Technical competence: A spatial vision good but maybe less directly relevant than weather assessment. D problem solving but moody/loner.\n\nThus provisional preference B.\n\nWe should note uncertainties: communication style could be problematic; we lack info on actual teamwork performance; need more info from others about candidate strengths we lack (e.g., maybe D's problem solving is exceptional). Ask others for more details on teamwork/communication for each candidate.\n\nWe must output PUBLIC_MESSAGE summarizing.\n\nProceed."}
