osphere? However guidelines say not to mitigate without evidence. But we have both positive and negative. We must weigh seriousness. For safety, reliability and decision-making are top. So I will provisionally favor Candidate C.\n\nWe must note uncertainties: severity of communication difficulty and egocentric attitude; whether B's pretentiousness and nasty remarks cause crew issues; A's health and leadership vs interpersonal; D's problem solving vs temperament.\n\nWhat would change vote: evidence that B's communication issues are minor and his technical strengths outweigh; or evidence that C's communication problems cause safety concerns; or new positive teamwork info for D or A.\n\nNow produce public message.\n\nMETADATA_JSON with vote \"Candidate C\"."}
